gobblin.metrics.reporter

Class OutputStreamReporter.Builder<T extends MetricReportReporter.Builder<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.metrics.reporter.MetricReportReporter.Builder<T>
      • gobblin.metrics.reporter.OutputStreamReporter.Builder<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OutputStreamReporter.BuilderImpl
    Enclosing class:
    OutputStreamReporter

    public abstract static class OutputStreamReporter.Builder<T extends MetricReportReporter.Builder<T>>
extends MetricReportReporter.Builder<T>
    A builder for OutputStreamReporter instances. Defaults to using the default locale and time zone, writing to System.out, converting rates to events/second, converting durations to milliseconds, and not filtering metrics.
